## Monitoring Patterns Observed
- **Recurring Issues**: Meta/Facebook service integrations frequently cause incidents across multiple platforms (Infobip, Klaviyo, Tidio, HubSpot, Intercom)
- **Payment Processing**: dLocal and similar services show periodic degradation
- **Communication Services**: Twilio, Sinch, Plivo, Bandwidth show recurring delivery/delay issues
- **Security Services**: Elastic Security, Rapid7 InsightIDR, Qualys, Atera experience periodic access/throttling issues
- **Weather Correlation**: Severe weather in Chicago area often precedes increased system monitoring activity

## System Health Maintenance
- All cron jobs consistently healthy (6-7 jobs verified each heartbeat)
- PulseWatch monitoring consistently tracks 50+ open incidents across services
- Standard vigilance maintained through automated heartbeat system
- Regular verification of system enhancements and improvements

